Generic single-database configuration with an async dbapi.

This is a simple migrations management system for the Soccer Tournament Management System.

To create a new migration:
```
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"
```

To upgrade to the latest migration:
```
alembic upgrade head
```

To downgrade to a previous migration:
```
alembic downgrade -1  # Go back one revision
alembic downgrade <revision>  # Go back to a specific revision
``` 